{"tid":2180950,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[識玩] 印度邀請俄羅斯加入美國主導的印太倡議","createTime":"2020-08-30T08:55:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-08T11:09:27.000Z","uid":267881,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"de7cef89beaa4a0d269d0a9249f99a2d6dd130e0","tid":2180950,"uid":267881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T08:55:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.epochtimes.com/b5/20/8/30/n12367121.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.epochtimes.com%2Fb5%2F20%2F8%2F30%2Fn12367121.htm&d=XjGeTWWNN7bjI%2BfZ7PvsLB9HEPLFM%2Fpg3GuXTgQF%2FE0%3D&h=8362b7cd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.epochtimes.com/b5/20/8/30/n12367121.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n中、俄兩國高層關係密切，習近平與普京自2013年以來，已經會晤了三十多次。雙方高層也多次對外宣稱中俄的「夥伴關係」。<br />\n<br />\n但近期，俄羅斯推遲交付中共軍火，卻加快交付印度於2018年訂購的5套S-400導彈。此舉雖使中俄關係受到關注，但是印度8月份的舉動使得中俄關係變得更加微妙。<br />\n<br />\n8月初，外媒報導，印度駐俄羅斯大使瓦瑪（Bala Venkatesh Varma）已向俄國副外相莫爾古洛夫（Igor Morgulov）提出邀約，邀請俄羅斯加入美國主導的印太倡議（Indo-Pacific Initiative），該組織被視為旨在聯合印太國家，反制中共。<br />\n<br />\n在中印邊境發生衝突後不久，俄羅斯已向印度出售33架戰機，並且更新原先賣給印度的戰機裝備。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a3875784ee891149d1f0beec36673eb85784c67","tid":2180950,"uid":2054,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T08:55:55.000Z","msg":"當中國狗咁撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eddddfdba84121bbe37a19e5289ff81ee30cd5a4","tid":2180950,"uid":343361,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T08:58:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bca197596b263132f7b306a53d26727e3f348425","tid":2180950,"uid":259812,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T09:03:39.000Z","msg":"世界第二變第三，畀著我就同支支覆桌啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22c0623240c38afce31831ccbc69ebdb11ba7597","tid":2180950,"uid":100986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T09:56:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f11934a1ce48b7289fb4b45f6c779371c005402d","tid":2180950,"uid":88737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T10:06:39.000Z","msg":"契哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"557cbe9a766e8ae361d57405d24957d7b6c69aa1","tid":2180950,"uid":346701,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T11:00:28.000Z","msg":"俄羅斯：唔想妨礙支那抗疫，暫停軍事武器送貨<br />\n支那：暖心"},{"pid":"9de78a2f69786cece55fe034d2d12faa5b4fe39b","tid":2180950,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T11:02:14.000Z","msg":"俄印同盟<br />\n<br />\n聯手對付中國"},{"pid":"f7b466dbe025381f12a2bcc566ab7d623f0ab85f","tid":2180950,"uid":253016,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"557cbe9a766e8ae361d57405d24957d7b6c69aa1","tid":2180950,"uid":346701,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T11:00:28.000Z","msg":"俄羅斯：唔想妨礙支那抗疫，暫停軍事武器送貨<br />\n支那：暖心"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T11:02:32.000Z","msg":"核平更暖心"},{"pid":"ee589232beae5198d21fd0d6df519c6892b63815","tid":2180950,"uid":59461,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T11:06:00.000Z","msg":"美國:想拉俄羅斯圍中，但國內好多人憎俄，就咁拉會比人屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n印度:我要拉埋俄黎圍中<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de96f31f48d0570fb03a0d03838a0892423f2131","tid":2180950,"uid":143241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3a3875784ee891149d1f0beec36673eb85784c67","tid":2180950,"uid":2054,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T08:55:55.000Z","msg":"當中國狗咁撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T11:08:10.000Z","msg":"點撚樣睇到撚支那啊,依家係邀請俄羅斯入去抗衡美國咋,我覺得."},{"pid":"7a08dbe5d85b02eab864404a866b239299f411ab","tid":2180950,"uid":349778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"202